item.title: CVE-2023-46135|2024-09-10T15:06:21.577Z -- stellar -- rs-stellar-strkey
item.description: rs-stellar-strkey is a Rust lib for encode/decode of Stellar Strkeys. A panic vulnerability occurs when a specially crafted payload is used.`inner_payload_len` should not above 64. This vulnerability has been patched in version 0.0.8.
